This script processes NetCDF sets to produce DSSAT-style ascii weather files. 
Its set up to run with 8 threads on pads. 

--------------------------------------------------------

1. compile using ./compile

2. edit "env" to change data directories, start and end year, etc.
   -Directory out_dir should already exist and be empty. 
   
3. run by executing ./run

[ 4. cleanup directory using ./cleanup ]

[ 5. can change walltime in PBS script by editing submit.start ]

